long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Btc Transaction Exporter is a chrome extension that exports bitcoin transaction history in csv.

Sites such as mempool allow you to view transaction history in your browser, but do not provide the ability to save history.

This extension is to help those who like Bitcoin and Ordinals to enjoy the activity more and save time on administrative work.

Please refer to the documentation for usage.

https://btctransactionexporter.gitbook.io/docs/
